    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《蜂巢与寻觅》是一款横版策略类基地建造游戏，玩家需要清除被怪物侵扰的空间站。通过集结机器人并清除各类危险区域，逐步摧毁蜂巢，逐块夺回空间站。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/bc64c1ac863686c210ce5b59cc432603.avif?t=1772140536\" width=600 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你监管下的一些空间站感染了一种奇怪的太空怪物，你与机组人员失去了联系，你的任务是回到空间站，通过摧毁每一个怪物蜂巢来夺回它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索舱室并从空间站废墟中打捞资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/aba793259fe9ff1801ff8bbca12add13.poster.avif?t=1772140536\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/aba793259fe9ff1801ff8bbca12add13.webm?t=1772140536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/aba793259fe9ff1801ff8bbca12add13.mp4?t=1772140536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构筑防御工事，修复建筑，夺回空间站。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/8b1d2df77952986c53b5c54bb48a9eb1.poster.avif?t=1772140536\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/8b1d2df77952986c53b5c54bb48a9eb1.webm?t=1772140536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/8b1d2df77952986c53b5c54bb48a9eb1.mp4?t=1772140536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建、集结并部署你的机器人军团，抵御一波波怪物的进攻。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/c7b4e119c34c3e99681f7ae732112254.poster.avif?t=1772140536\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/c7b4e119c34c3e99681f7ae732112254.webm?t=1772140536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/c7b4e119c34c3e99681f7ae732112254.mp4?t=1772140536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >搜寻并剿灭怪物巢穴，彻底解除其对空间站的控制。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/1ae118f3f9a4241d77e9f8b9709cabb1.poster.avif?t=1772140536\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/1ae118f3f9a4241d77e9f8b9709cabb1.webm?t=1772140536\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2193110/extras/1ae118f3f9a4241d77e9f8b9709cabb1.mp4?t=1772140536\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特点: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔ 逐个夺回你的空间站。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤖 战斗一波又一波独特的怪物，它们正盘踞在你的站点上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔨 锤炼核心基础设施，打造你的机器人军团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 通过建造并部署机器人到墙壁上来保卫你的基地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⌛ 60-90分钟的进程。</p>",
